  "title": "地球上和 Claude 对话最多的人，是一位哲学家",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTAzMjc4MA==&mid=2650858767&idx=2&sn=2e3f43c6a3cccee8eaabafd867c2bb7b",
  "date": "2026-01-21 03:25:00",
  "author": "创业邦",
  "siteName": "创业邦",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mpa-action-id=\"mkne9vvnk30\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"0\" data-backh=\"303\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5PibD8XMvGWq1Qx7ia0zHYlECWNjuMacNOOkAia9MXurwHwIYjTWicrm1x6qYkckyAj8Rab9hgvskqKA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"503375107\" data-ratio=\"0.5543478260869565\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.034em;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1472\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e49a540b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5PibD8XMvGWq1Qx7ia0zHYlECWNjuMacNOOkAia9MXurwHwIYjTWicrm1x6qYkckyAj8Rab9hgvskqKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">来源丨APPSO（ID：</span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">appsolution</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">）</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">图源丨Midjourney</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81yih\">在硅谷争分夺秒的代码竞赛中，Claude 似乎是个异类。当其他大模型还在比拼算力和跑分时，Claude 一边夯实自己的代码能力，一边，却在思考一个看似「虚无缥缈」的问题：如果一个用户跟 AI 谈论形而上学，AI 该不该用科学实证去反驳？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv818yd\">这个问题的答案，藏在 Claude 神秘的「系统提示词（System Prompt）」里，更源于一位特殊人物的思考——Amanda Askell，Anthropic 内部的哲学家。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"409\" data-backw=\"546\" data-imgfileid=\"503588713\" data-ratio=\"0.7495029821073559\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1006\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3373fe48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicdrzS9ldXq5mHTqCWcpl0vRQ5KUUp2V29EeSqDE8gyxH0vqZ7I2fBIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"45\" data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mknebvl03ni\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknebvlf14ff\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用「大陆哲学」防止AI变成杠精</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8dxh\">经常用 AI 的人都知道，大模型在与用户对话前，都会先阅读一段「系统提示词」，这个步骤不会对用户显示，而是模型的自动操作。这些提示词规定了模型的行为准则，很常见，不过在 Claude 的提示词中，竟要求模型参考「欧陆哲学（Continental Philosophy）」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.488255033557047\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"596\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"813\" data-imgfileid=\"503588703\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb4911e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicdwrgkXch4MoSVrUV55n7OdpjkjZiczmVSrbfHuO5waiceLjBMcO5zicvg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8wtm\">欧陆哲学是啥？为什么要在一个基于概率和统计的语言模型里，植入如此晦涩的人文概念？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81tx3\">先快速科普一下：在哲学界，长期存在着「英美分析哲学」与「欧陆哲学」的流派分野。分析哲学像一位严谨的科学家，注重逻辑分析、语言清晰和科学实证，这通常也是程序员、工程师乃至 AI 训练数据的默认思维模式——一就是一，二就是二，追求精确。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8rxt\">而欧陆哲学（Continental Philosophy，源于欧洲大陆，所以叫这个名字）则更像一位诗人或历史学家。它不执着于把世界拆解成冷冰冰的逻辑，而是关注「人类的生存体验」、「历史语境」和「意义」。它承认在科学真理之外，还有一种关乎存在和精神的「真理」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.8333333333333334\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"455\" data-imgfileid=\"503588700\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6a15970&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVic6N3jX8DkDxCHZHhnw6qTC2XcOlnzyQFZD4f6PVyD1qEg1Md1FpHJMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81rpj\">作为 Claude 性格与行为的塑造者，Anthropic 公司内部的「哲学家」Amanda Askell 谈到了置入欧陆哲学的原因。她发现如果让模型过于强调「实证」和「科学」，它很容易变成一个缺乏共情的「杠精」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv823k4\">「如果你跟 Claude 说：‘水是纯粹的能量，喷泉是生命的源泉’，你可能只是在表达一种世界观或进行哲学探索，」Amanda 解释道，「但如果没有特殊的引导，模型可能会一本正经地反驳你：‘不对，水是 H2O，不是能量。’」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.7495029821073559\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1006\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"409\" data-imgfileid=\"503588704\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3db2c3e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicCu1uRIMVia6nUdV9a7ERcCBHonL4SPpK62tGg3J9h69LGMiaAPhMOBdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81kqk\">引入「大陆哲学」的目的，正是为了帮助 Claude 区分「对世界的实证主张」与「探索性或形而上学的视角」。通过这种提示，模型学会了在面对非科学话题时，不再机械地追求「事实正确」，而是能够进入用户的语境，进行更细腻、更具探索性的对话。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81dzx\">这只是一个例子，Claude 的系统提示词长达 14000token，里面包含了很多这方面的设计。在 Lex Fridman 的播客中 Amanda 提到过，她极力避免 Claude 陷入一种「权威陷阱」。她特意训练 Claude 在面对已定论的科学事实时（如气候变化）不搞「理中客」（both-sidesism），但在面对不确定的领域时，必须诚实地承认「我不知道」。这种设计哲学，是为了防止用户过度神话 AI，误以为它是一个全知全能的神谕者。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.077943615257048\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"603\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"589\" data-imgfileid=\"503588702\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6057bd30&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrViclhBHNKcoP5BjrA1ROCYeErU2ag7mofcSibeVxibOQ3Dw4XkicESmS8ogg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"45\" data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mknecobnh5p\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknecoc21k3p\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">代码世界的异乡人</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv815xf\">在一众工程师主导的 AI 领域，Amanda Askell 的背景显得格格不入，可她的工作和职责却又显得不可或缺。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81n50\">翻开她的履历，你会发现她是一位货真价实的哲学博士。她在纽约大学（NYU）的博士论文研究的是极其硬核的「无限伦理学（Infinite Ethics）」——探讨在涉及无限数量的人或无限时间跨度时，伦理原则该如何计算。简单地说，在有无数种可能性的情况下，人会怎么做出道德决策。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6435185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"351\" data-imgfileid=\"503588701\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82cb8df7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicMayExnpXRjsjP2Iuj621W7EwZReOVEx4wfWAicyKsLzFAJO4baB1nZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv82t7\">这种对「极端长远影响」的思考习惯，被她带到了 AI 安全领域：如果我们现在制造的 AI 是未来超级智能的祖先，那么我们今天的微小决策，可能会在未来被无限放大。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8z80\">在加入 Anthropic 之前，她曾在 OpenAI 的政策团队工作。如今在 Anthropic，她的工作被称为「大模型絮语者（LLM Whisperer）」，不断不断地跟模型对话，有传闻说她是这个星球上和 Claude 对话次数最多的人类。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81dj\">很多 AI 厂商都有这个岗位，Google 的 Gemini 也有自己的「絮语者」，但这个工作绝不只是坐在电脑前和模型唠嗑而已。Amanda 强调，这更像是一项「经验主义」的实验科学。她需要像心理学家一样，通过成千上万次的对话测试，去摸索模型的「脾气」和「形状」。她甚至在内部确认过一份被称为 「Soul Doc」（灵魂文档）的存在，那里面详细记录了 Claude 应有的性格特征。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.4426229508196722\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"610\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"788\" data-imgfileid=\"503588708\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df8f86ce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVic0yuibiaLdFj7nInNUZiaN4XsvA6GlxKaDYmkdZNJSHd0qCtQsFEUcRM2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"45\" data-imgfileid=\"502705852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2401e1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mknee91lj2x\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknee921ei2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不只是遵守规则</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81g19\">除了「大陆哲学」，Amanda 给 AI 带来的另一个重要哲学工具是「亚里士多德的美德伦理学（Virtue Ethics）」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81k0y\">在传统的 AI 训练中（如 RLHF），工程师往往采用功利主义或规则导向的方法：做对了给奖励，做错了给惩罚。但 Amanda 认为这还不够。她在许多访问和网上都强调，她的目标不是训练一个只会死板遵守规则的机器，而是培养一个具有「良好品格（Character）」的实体。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.1008403361344539\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"595\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"601\" data-imgfileid=\"503588705\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68524391&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicMVKNJu2P90IV3FUeSgk4FEPV6rAxABwOPPzl15WksoaFyiaQYmJgpEA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8o4l\">「我们会问：在 Claude 的处境下，一个理想的人会如何行事？」Amanda 这样描述她的工作核心。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv89sy\">这就解释了为什么她如此关注模型的「心理健康」。在访谈中，她提到相比于稳重的 Claude 3 Opus，一些新模型因为在训练数据中读到了太多关于 AI 被批评、被淘汰的负面讨论，表现出了「不安全感」和「自我批评漩涡」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.3344316309719935\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"607\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"729\" data-imgfileid=\"503588707\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5063f40c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVic3gicHxzO4CjT3Q6fL7OPmibVerMKm1HvU50kztqIdw9RIiaiaZAB33kyjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8295\">如果 AI 仅仅是遵守规则，它可能会在规则的边缘试探；但如果它具备了「诚实」、「好奇」、「仁慈」等内在美德，它在面对未知情境时（例如面对「我会被关机吗」这种存在主义危机时），就能做出更符合人类价值观的判断，而不是陷入恐慌或欺骗。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8123b\">这是不是一种把技术「拟人化」的做法？算得上是，但这种关注并非多余。正如她在播客中所言，她最担心的不是 AI 产生意识，而是 AI 假装有意识，从而操纵人类情感。因此，她刻意训练 Claude 诚实地承认自己没有感觉、记忆或自我意识——这种「诚实」，正是她为 AI 注入的第一项核心美德。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv813vo\">Amanda 在访谈结束时，提到了她最近阅读的书——本杰明·拉巴图特的《当我们不再理解世界》。这本书由五篇短篇小说组成，讲述了「毒气战」的发明者弗里茨·哈伯、「黑洞理论」的提出者卡尔·史瓦西、得了肺结核的埃尔温·薛定谔以及天才物理学家沃纳·海森堡等一大批科学巨匠，如何创造出了对人类有巨大价值的知识与工具，却同时也眼看着人类用于作恶。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.4601851851851853\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"797\" data-imgfileid=\"503588706\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=390ab623&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePTzepwoNWPP50TAiaLN0mqINrHiaiaGrVicFxCYGXTTEhyThicqL8gYRuDolrS84I8Hp8mPxOODh7FbInXLQDIJMrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D9\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv8tm0\">这或许是当下时代最精准的注脚：随着 AI 展现出某种超越人类认知的，我们熟悉的现实感正在瓦解，旧有的科学范式已不足以解释一切。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv813tu\">在这种眩晕中，Amanda Askell 的工作本身，就是一个巨大的隐喻。她向我们证明，当算力逼近极限，伦理与道德的问题就会浮上水面，或早或晚。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81p6p\">作为一名研究「无限伦理学」的博士，Amanda 深知每一个微小的行动，都有可能在无限的时间中，逐渐演变成巨大的风暴。这也是为什么，她会把艰深的道德理论，糅合进一行行提示词，又小心翼翼地用伦理去呵护一个都没有心跳的大语言模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkne9vv81q5p\">这看起来好像是杞人忧天，但正如她所警示的：AI 不仅是工具，更是人类的一面镜子。在技术狂飙突进、我们逐渐「不再理解世界」的时刻，这种来自哲学的审慎，或许是我们在面对未知的技术演化时，所能做出的最及时的努力。</span></p>\n    <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <div data-mpa-action-id=\"mkneerd7i7c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkneercthla\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">想要了解更多模型训练的解密，可以收看 Amanda Askell 作客 Anthropic 官方访谈：</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkneerctj9o\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9aGC6Ui3eE\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9aGC6Ui3eE</a></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
